  "texts": [
    "Since students use GenAI responsibly, this scenario is assumed to be the base scenario.",
    "In this scenario, educators should integrate GenAI tools into their lectures to provide students with use cases of these tools.",
    "They could implement feedback mechanisms for students to provide input on their experiences with GenAI tools, allowing for continuous improvement.",
    "They need to ensure that AI-powered resources and materials are accessible and promote digital literacy among students.",
    "Furthermore, educators need to regularly evaluate the impact and effectiveness of GenAI tools in achieving educational goals and be prepared to adapt and evolve strategies as GenAI technologies continue to develop and the usage behavior of students could change."
  ],
